性验证\\n- 格式校验\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**3. 数据存储**\\n- 加密存储（AES-256）\\n- 访问控制（RBAC）\\n- 审计日志\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**4. 数据处理**\\n- 不存储原始输入（可选用）\\n- 定期删除历史数据\\n- 匿名化处理\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"6\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**示例：PII检测与脱敏**\\n```\\n输入：\\\"我的手机号是13812345678\\\"\\n检测：识别11位手机号\\n脱敏：\\\"我的手机号是138****5678\\\"\\n```\"}]]}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}]\n1c:T7bf,import re\nfrom typing import List, Tuple\n\nclass PIIDetector:\n    \"\"\"敏感信息检测与脱敏\"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.patterns = {\n            \"phone\": (r'1[3-9]\\d{9}', self._mask_phone),\n            \"id_card\": (r'\\d{17}[\\dXx]', self._mask_id_card),\n            \"email\": (r'[\\w.-]+@[\\w.-]+\\.\\w+', self._mask_email),\n            \"credit_card\": (r'\\d{13,19}', self._mask_credit_card),\n        }\n\n    def detect_and_mask(self, text: str) -> Tuple[str, List[dict]]:\n        \"\"\"检测并脱敏敏感信息\"\"\"\n        masked_text = text\n        detected = []\n\n        for pii_type, (pattern, mask_func) in self.patterns.items():\n            matches = re.findall(pattern, text)\n            for match in matches:\n                # 记录检测结果\n                detected.append({\n                    \"type\": pii_type,\n                    \"value\": match,\n                    \"position\": text.find(match)\n                })\n                # 脱敏处理\n                masked_value = mask_func(match)\n                masked_text = masked_text.replace(match, masked_value, 1)\n\n        return masked_text, detected\n\n    def _mask_phone(self, phone: str) -> str:\n        \"\"\"手机号脱敏：138****5678\"\"\"\n        return phone[:3] + \"****\" + phone[-4:]\n\n    def _mask_id_card(self, id_card: str) -> str:\n        \"\"\"身份证脱敏：110***********1234\"\"\"\n        return id_card[:3] + \"***********\" + id_card[-4:]\n\n    def _mask_email(self, email: str) -> str:\n        \"\"\"邮箱脱敏：a***@example.com\"\"\"\n        parts = email.split(\"@\")\n        return parts[0][0] + \"***@\" + parts[1]\n\n    def _mask_credit_card(self, card: str) -> str:\n        \"\"\"银行卡脱敏：**** **** **** 1234\"\"\"\n        return \"**** **** **** \" + card[-4:]\n\n# 使用示例\ndetector = PIIDetector()\ntext = \"我的手机是13812345678，邮箱是zhang@example.com\"\nmasked, detected = detector.detect_and_mask(text)\nprint(masked)\n# 输出：我的手机是138****5678，邮箱是z***@example.com15:[\"$\",\"div\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"mb-8 last:mb-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm\",\"children\":4}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900\",\"children\":\"代码示例：敏感信息检测\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"实现PII检测和脱敏：\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 bg-gray-900 rounded-lg overflow-hidden\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center justify-between px-4 py-2 bg-gray-800 border-b border-gray-700\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-gray-400 font-mono\",\"children\":\"python\"}]}],[\"$\",\"pre\",null,{\"className\":\"p-4 overflow-x-auto\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"code\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-gray-100 font-mono whitespace-pre\",\"children\":\"$1c\"}]}]]}],\"$undefined\"]}]\n16:[\"$\",\"div\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"mb-8 last:mb-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm\",\"children\":5}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900\",\"children\":\"合规要求\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**主要法规**：\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**1. 《个人信息保护法》（中国）**\\n- 明确告知用户信息用途\\n- 获得用户同意\\n- 提供删除和导出功能\\n- 数据出境审批\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**2. GDPR（欧盟）**\\n- 用户有权访问、更正、删除数据\\n- 数据最小化原则\\n- 隐私保护设计（Privacy by Design）\\n- 72小时内报告数据泄露\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"3\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**3. 《数据安全法》（中国）**\\n- 数据分类分级\\n- 重要数据保护\\n- 数据安全评估\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"4\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**AI特定合规**：\\n- 《生成式人工智能服务管理暂行办法》（中国）\\n- 内容审核要求\\n- 算法备案\\n- 安全评估报告\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**认证标准**：\\n- ISO 27001：信息安全管理体系\\n- SOC 2：服务组织控制\\n- 等保2.0：网络安全等级保护\"}]]}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}]\n17:[\"$\",\"div\",\"5\",{\"className\":\"mb-8 last:mb-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm\",\"children\":6}],[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900\",\"children\":\"实战：企业合规检查清单\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",\"0\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**数据收集阶段**：\\n- [ ] 隐私政策已更新，明确说明数据用途\\n- [ ] 用户同意机制已实现（勾选框、弹窗）\\n- [ ] 数据收集最小化，不收集无关信息\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"1\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**数据处理阶段**：\\n- [ ] 敏感信息自动检测和脱敏\\n- [ ] 数据加密存储\\n- [ ] 访问控制已配置\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",\"2\",{\"className\":\"whitespace-pre-line\",\"children\":\"**数据存储阶段**：\\n- [ ] 存储加密（传输和静止）\\n- [ ] 备份机制完善\\n- [ ] 保留期限设置\"}],[\"$\",\"p